&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity to work in a Adult Autism Diagnostic service. You will develop skills in the diagnosis and management of adults with Autism plus or minus co morbid mental health needs. It is an ideal post for a psychiatry with experience in general adult or learning disabilities.You will be well supported bu the consultant and MDT. It is a part-time post and there are opportunities to add extra sessions in other teams if interested in more hours.&lt;/p&gt;
